Safe Paste
==========

A fork of NoPaste (https://github.com/bokub/nopaste) by Boris K, which is based
on topaz/paste (https://github.com/topaz/paste). Licensed under MIT (see LICENSE).

Third-party libraries (loaded from jsDelivr, cached for offline by the service
worker):
  - lz-string      (MIT)  — URL-safe compression
  - EasyMDE         (MIT)  — markdown editor
  - marked          (MIT)  — markdown rendering
  - DOMPurify       (Apache-2.0 / MPL-2.0) — HTML sanitization
  - highlight.js    (BSD-3-Clause) — code syntax highlighting
